snippet.title: Buried - Official Trailer [Authogin]
snippet.description:
The official trailer for Buried by Authogin, out October 30, 2023! A short horror game that takes place entirely inside a casket. You wake up buried alive. You are running out of oxygen and you can't remember how you got here. There must be a way out, can you figure it out in time?

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2605640/Buried/
Wishlist today!

Twitter: https:// twitter.com/authogin
Twitch: https:// www.twitch.tv/authogin
